Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#12 ONE NlGHT STAND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡力林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算世界滅亡了\N那大叔也不會死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陸上自衛隊的96式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅麗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅麗莎\N用單分子切割刀瞄準姆指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在正…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅麗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入-Driver，B機能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，來試看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，就是盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有發現到我對妳的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍的泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果在那個時候\N殺了琢磨的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人就會放棄啟動那架貝希摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然得不到，那就摧毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰莎，坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來推，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你駕駛了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校大人，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校大人，增援呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想辦法解決那個巨人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能逃得出我的手掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能夠阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，真高興您沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬德加斯，現在潛艦來到哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀伊半島南方120公里附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急配置的噴射器也在射程外\N(AS射出用裝置)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用彈道飛彈把Arbalest(強弩兵)送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備時間最少也要花一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在送達前的這一兩個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個巨人貝希摩斯不知道\N會給這城市帶來多大的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒辦法，我已經無計可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，現在的情勢\N需要Arbalest(強弩兵)嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就發射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有得到您許可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是載有Arbalest(強弩兵)的彈道飛彈\N已經準備好可在3分鐘內發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射後約6分鐘\N大概就能抵達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N需要花費9分鐘的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已有覺悟接受處罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落地點呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落後可能會隨即遭到巨人攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更複雜的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸後能夠爭取出數十秒的時間\N讓駕駛可以過去搭乘的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視野不要太遼闊比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不能在鬧區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把平民捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照明較暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且是限定的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最好也能有高低差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠充分發揮\NArbalest(強弩兵)能力的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它要開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到我叫你就轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它再瞄準一點打過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小貨車可是撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，讓車子一直線向前跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那傢伙一點顏色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎，絕對要一直線喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度也不要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，瞄準我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右頭部火神砲損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘爆迴避完畢\N我…我的貝希摩斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右頭部火神砲無法使用\N竟敢傷了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯茲好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你只是個\N光說不練的軟弱傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要安心還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝希摩斯…啟動了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，妳贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破壞它是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料可以撐40個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，沒人能夠阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要看琢磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得對不起他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為記憶混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時竟把我當成\N被他親手殺死的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就憑著這點利用了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有親人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不問我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那種好像什麼都知道的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直讓人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我你的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德魯・賽格維奇・卡力林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，還以為死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝吧，衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間笑的話就再開一槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣動來動去怎麼射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，之前也有看過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，被看得清清楚楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體不會這麼簡單就壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉彎，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，會怎樣我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛6號呼叫野牛7號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是野牛7號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在拖拖拉拉個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手動操縱桿被壓在地板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法強制打開容器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法打破蛋殼是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變成炒蛋的話\N就都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要詛咒你\N直到你的子孫十八代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有最後一枚手榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這試看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面，裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝破鐵捲門進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也有過這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃吧，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入-Driver，A機能低落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨骼系發生干擾波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，得集中精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良宗介在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會去問你姊姊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在獵物面前舔舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是三流的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當你的對手，過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣才能…好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷卻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要，拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巨人的其中一個冷卻裝置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES，士官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架機體有搭載入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設敵機有搭載入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可以對抗它的手段嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以現場士官的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把意識…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右膝蓋連接部損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我搞不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過腳的連結部分好像有\N入-Driver的冷卻裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊那個地方，大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不能用普通的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上校大人說的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說泰莎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的回答怎麼這麼隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要覺得很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來所要發射的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會貫穿它的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼的相信才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，就像那個時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一條細長的隙縫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右哪邊都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會中…一定要打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入-Driver機能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回復的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝希摩斯因重量過重開始分解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了，姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這種事有時也會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，的確很過份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，安心的入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的技術還是一樣的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架機體已經是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你好好珍惜它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…小要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要特別感謝妳才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳真這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳能好好說明一下這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，改天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我能跟妳宣言一件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良士官\N把聽覺感應器全部關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像喜歡上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…我…\N泰莎，泰莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是跟妳說一聲\N“我們互相加油吧”好了，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃紅豆飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡力林他們似乎平安無事喔

